query: SELECT p.id, p.name, p.slug, a.name as atoll_name FROM places p LEFT JOIN atolls a ON p.atollId = a.id WHERE a.name = 'Alif Dhaal Atoll' AND p.type = 'island' ORDER BY p.name LIMIT 50
